🌟 Daily Companion – Your All-in-One Productivity Assistant

------------------------------------------------------------
📦 INSTALLATION GUIDE (NO PYTHON REQUIRED)
------------------------------------------------------------

Thank you for downloading the **Daily Companion** app!

This is a beta version of a lightweight productivity desktop app that helps you:
✅ Track daily goals
📝 Take quick notes
🍅 Stay focused using Pomodoro sessions
📅 Use calendar, reminders, expense tracker & more!

------------------------------------------------------------
📁 How to Use:
------------------------------------------------------------
1. Extract the ZIP file to any location on your computer.
2. Double-click on the file named:
   ➤ DailyCompanion.exe
3. No installation needed. The app runs instantly.
4. The app will create a folder named `user_data` beside it.
   This folder stores all your tasks, goals, and settings locally.

------------------------------------------------------------
⚠️ Important Notes:
------------------------------------------------------------
• This is a standalone version — you do NOT need Python installed.
• All data is saved locally — no internet or login required.
• Your first launch will show a short tutorial and productivity summary.
• If Windows Defender shows a warning, click **"More Info" → "Run Anyway"** (common for unsigned apps).

------------------------------------------------------------
