------------------------------------------------------------
💡 Tips:
------------------------------------------------------------
• Set your daily goals in the mentor tab.
• Use the Pomodoro timer for focused work sessions.
• Click around the side menu to explore all features.
• Run the app daily to build your streak and earn badges!

